<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A new company wants to be the <a href="//www.fastcoexist.com/3028877/change-generation/now-you-can-file-for-divorce-online-with-wevorce-the-hr-block-of-nasty-bre">H&amp;R Block</a> of divorce. <span id="more-84672"></span></p>
